snippet.title: Bye Sweet Carole - Midnight Trailer
snippet.description:
We're proud to share with you the latest update on Bye Sweet Carole that you have been able to discover during the Indie Horror Showcase from DreadXP! Thank you for hosting the event and having us on board ♥

Bye Sweet Carole will launch in 2025 on Steam, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series. 

Discover more on https://www.byesweetcarole.com
